Название задачи: center of Europe
Категория задачи: OSINT
Сложность: medium
They say Europe has 2 centers: one was found by the French - 54°50′ north latitude and 25°19′ east longitude. The other one is on this monument - 55°30′ north latitude and 28°48′ east longitude. And what are the coordinates of the center of Europe to which this monument refers?
